text: Neža Černe (born 1933) is a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Maribor
